
一、环境配置

1. 下载[jdk8](https://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html)
2. 配置[环境变量](https://blog.csdn.net/renlianggee/article/details/90023464)
3. 下载开发神器[IDEA](https://www.jetbrains.com/idea/download/#section=windows)

二、启动项目： 

 1. 创建数据库xlian_admin，执行sql脚本xlian_admin.sql
 2. 打开IDEA
    > ![QHHOlq.png](https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/12/18/QHHOlq.png)
               
    > ![QHHjXV.png](https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/12/18/QHHjXV.png)

 3. 等待项目初始化，然后点击启动
